R Function Flashcards Florian Reiche Department of Politics and International Studies, University of Warwick Last Updated 21.06.2024 Preface Welcome to the collection of flash cards which should help you to learn the purpose of R function on all POQ-coded modules in PAIS for which I am responsible. These are listed in the left-hand menu, and are subdivided by weekly content. The “Module” Section at the end tests all functions employed on the module. If you have any queries, please contact me under F.Reiche@warwick.ac.uk And now, I hope you enjoy the module!
